      <title>今明两年澳洲房价可能上涨5.0%</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/australia-home-prices-likely-rise-50-this-year-next-2024-02-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[路透社的一项民意调查显示，房地产分析师继续预测 2024 年澳大利亚房价将上涨 5.0%，这驳回了自三个月前上次民意调查以来央行发表的评论，即年底前可能加息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/australia-home-prices-likely-rise-50-this-year-next-2024-02-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 03:31:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国称其海警在台湾岛屿周围巡逻“无可非议”</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-its-coast-guard-patrols-around-taiwan-islands-beyond-reproach-2024-02-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国政府周三表示，中国海警在中国海岸附近的台湾岛屿周围的巡逻“无可非议”，并驳回了有关台湾游船登船引发恐慌的抱怨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-its-coast-guard-patrols-around-taiwan-islands-beyond-reproach-2024-02-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 03:21:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>2023年韩国生育率降至历史新低</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-koreas-fertility-rate-dropped-fresh-record-low-2023-2024-02-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国的生育率已经是世界上最低的，2023年却跌至历史新低，尽管该国花费了数十亿美元试图扭转人口连续第四年萎缩的趋势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-koreas-fertility-rate-dropped-fresh-record-low-2023-2024-02-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 03:03:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度尼西亚推定总统普拉博沃被授予最高军事荣誉</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesias-presumed-president-prabowo-awarded-highest-military-honour-2024-02-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度尼西亚即将卸任的总统周三授予他的假定继任者、前特种部队指挥官普拉博沃·苏比安托(Prabowo Subianto)该国最高军事荣誉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesias-presumed-president-prabowo-awarded-highest-military-honour-2024-02-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 02:55:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国通胀测试即将到来，亚洲股市走势缓慢；猕猴桃幻灯片</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-02-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三，在美国本周公布的通胀数据可能会影响美联储宽松周期的时机之前，亚洲股市周三表现谨慎，而在央行软化利率鹰派立场后，新西兰元大幅下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-02-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 02:33:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国称北京和莫斯科应加强亚太协调</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-beijing-moscow-should-strengthen-coordination-asia-pacific-2024-02-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国外交部周三表示，中俄应加强在亚太事务中的沟通协调，共同维护地区安全、稳定和发展。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-beijing-moscow-should-strengthen-coordination-asia-pacific-2024-02-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 02:15:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新西兰央行维持利率不变，政策路线不再那么鹰派</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/nz-central-bank-holds-rates-says-policy-needs-stay-tight-while-2024-02-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新西兰央行周三将现金利率维持在 5.5% 不变，并下调了利率预测峰值，令市场感到意外，因为政策制定者表示通胀前景的风险已变得更加平衡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/nz-central-bank-holds-rates-says-policy-needs-stay-tight-while-2024-02-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 01:37:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚一月通胀保持在两年低位，关注二月数据</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/australias-inflation-holds-two-year-low-jan-2024-02-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管预测会上升，但澳大利亚 1 月份消费者价格通胀仍维持在两年低点，这强化了利率不太可能进一步上升的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/australias-inflation-holds-two-year-low-jan-2024-02-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 01:17:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>领取补贴大米的长队凸显了印度尼西亚穷人的困境</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/sprawling-queues-subsidised-rice-highlight-plight-indonesias-poor-2024-02-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[午后的阳光下，数十名印度尼西亚人（其中大部分是女性）排着蜿蜒的队列购买一袋袋补贴大米，他们的手臂伸进金属门去抢门票，以确保他们有一个购买的位置。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/sprawling-queues-subsidised-rice-highlight-plight-indonesias-poor-2024-02-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 01:02:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾总统称中国海军在南海的存在“令人担忧”</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-navys-presence-south-china-sea-is-worrisome-says-philippine-president-2024-02-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯周三表示，中国海军在南海的存在“令人担忧”，但不会阻止菲律宾保卫其海洋领土和保护其渔民。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-navys-presence-south-china-sea-is-worrisome-says-philippine-president-2024-02-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 00:48:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
